Architecture Pattern: Feature-Driven Modular Engine
- /src/core: Global state (Zustand), Supabase client, Auth.
- /src/shared/tools: Reusable stateless utilities/components (e.g., YuhConnector).
- /src/shared/components: Atomic UI elements (Buttons, Cards, Layouts).
- /src/features/[stage-id]: Stage-based folders containing Modules.

Data-Driven Module Rule:
- Every module must be a shell that renders tasks from tasks.config.ts.
- No hard-coded steps in UI. Task types: 'info' | 'input' | 'ai-coach' | 'tool-action'.

AI-Context Integration:
- Every major component must start with a standardized JSDoc header:
  /**
   * @MODULE_ID <string>
   * @STAGE <string>
   * @DATA_INPUTS <string[]>
   * @REQUIRED_TOOLS <string[]>
   */

Design System:
- Swiss FinTech minimal aesthetic.
- Colors: Slate-900 (primary), Emerald-500 (success), Yuh-inspired Pink/Red (actions).
- Global layout elements: Task-Progress-Bar, Toolbox-Sidebar.
